Invocation Name: pulso central
des:
Start by Saying: Alexa, play Pulso Central.
 
Pulso Central is the Central New York Region’s first and only Spanish-language audio service, from WCNY, member-supported public media. This skill allows Alexa users to listen live to the station anytime, to enjoy a wide variety of Latino music, plus local and national informational programming relevant to the region’s growing Hispanic community.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
